To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private CommodityChannelIndex _cci;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_cci = CCI(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_cci.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "typicalpriceaverage", _cci.TypicalPriceAverage.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "typicalpricemeandeviation", _cci.TypicalPriceMeanDeviation.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "commoditychannelindex", _cci.Current.Value);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.cci = self.CCI(symbol, period)

# In OnData()
if self.cci.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "typicalpriceaverage", self.cci.TypicalPriceAverage.Current.Value)
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "typicalpricemeandeviation", self.cci.TypicalPriceMeanDeviation.Current.Value)
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "commoditychannelindex", self.cci.Current.Value)
